$DIALOGUE Pronunciation: "then" vs "den"
REPEAT
INTRO: Read these word pairs aloud.
INSTRUCTION: Listen and repeat.

LINE: they / day
LINE: there / dare
LINE: then / den
LINE: though / dough
LINE: than / Dan

